<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>msẖ mmkn yrtạḥ qlbk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- msẖ mmkn yrtạḥ qlbk .. wạnt bʿyd ʿn rbk
 lw rbḥt ạlʿạlm klh .. msẖ hyryḥ qlbk
 (kl ạlʿạlm bạṭl .. klh qbḍ ạlryḥ)2
 (yạlly ʿạyz yrtạḥ qlbk .. tʿạly̱ llmsyḥ)2
 2- mhmạ tʿmr fy ạldnyạ .. bkrh lạbd tmwt
 ạ̹wʿy̱ ạlfrṣẗ tḍyʿ mnk .. ạ̹wʿy̱ ạlfrṣẗ tfwt
 (ạ̹smʿ ṣwt ạ̹lhk .. tʿạly̱ llmsyḥ)2
 (qwl lh ạ̹rḥmny ạ̉nạ ạlkẖạṭy .. fy lḥẓẗ tstryḥ)2
 3- wạnt msạfr ʿ ạlạ̉bdyẗ .. lạbd tkwn wyạk
 tdẖkrẗ ạlsfr mkẖtwmẗ .. bdm yswʿ mwlạk
 (kẖdhạ mnh ạlận .. lyfwt ạlạ̉wạn)2
 (trjʿ tndm wtḍyʿ mnk .. frṣẗ ạlgẖfrạn)2
 4- wạnt yạlly f kwrẗ bʿydẗ .. bʿd mạ knt ạ̉myr
 trjʿ tsẖthy ạlkẖrnwb .. ạlly btạklh ạlkẖnạzyr
 (kl ạlʿạlm fạny .. klh ạ̉nyn wdmwʿ)2
 (msẖ mmkn ysẖbʿ qlbk .. gẖyr ạlrb yswʿ)2</lyrics>
<author>jrjs mʿwḍ, jrjs mʿwḍ</author>
<hymn_number>843</hymn_number>
</song>